WEBVTT

00:08.808 --> 00:10.775
Ah, nothing.

00:10.810 --> 00:12.812
Well, so far,
it doesn't smell like a trap.

00:12.847 --> 00:14.814
Maybe this kid's
actually on the level.

00:15.215 --> 00:17.182
I can't blame
him for being careful.

00:17.217 --> 00:19.219
Considering how ashlocke
treats his friends,

00:19.619 --> 00:21.586
i don't even want to know
what he'd do to a defector.

00:21.621 --> 00:24.023
Well, before you bring out
your violin, let's just remember

00:24.058 --> 00:26.426
that nobody actually forced
the links to give themselves

00:26.461 --> 00:28.028
over to ashlocke.

00:28.063 --> 00:29.594
Really?

00:29.629 --> 00:31.631
Sure about that?

00:32.031 --> 00:33.633
Well, you know,
i'm just saying let's...

00:34.034 --> 00:36.036
just make sure that this guy
really wants to break free of

00:36.071 --> 00:38.438
this sociopath before
we let our guard down.

00:38.473 --> 00:39.656
Okay?

00:39.691 --> 00:40.840
Stop!

00:41.241 --> 00:43.643
Stay where i can see you!

00:51.651 --> 00:53.653
Sure you weren't followed?

00:53.688 --> 00:55.655
No, it's just us.

00:55.690 --> 00:58.823
What's up?

00:58.858 --> 01:00.460
I thought you said
there were more people want
to get away from ashlocke.

01:00.860 --> 01:02.427
Yeah, there were ten of us.

01:02.462 --> 01:04.063
Ashlocke got the others
before they could escape.

01:04.464 --> 01:06.031
I... i barely made it out.

01:06.066 --> 01:08.068
Like, i don't know what
he's going to do to them.

01:08.103 --> 01:10.035
You gotta help them get out.

01:10.070 --> 01:12.072
Well, yeah, but we need
to know a bit more first.

01:12.107 --> 01:13.638
Look, i don't
know what happened.

01:13.673 --> 01:15.675
It used to be about all of
us working together, you know?

01:15.710 --> 01:17.277
Now, it's just
all about gabriel.

01:18.878 --> 01:22.482
Look,
gabriel is really sick, but
he's still strong, all right?

01:22.517 --> 01:24.084
He's planning
something really big.

01:24.119 --> 01:25.685
He calls it his last testament.

01:25.720 --> 01:27.252
I don't know what it is.

01:27.287 --> 01:29.689
But whatever
it is, it scares me.

01:29.724 --> 01:32.092
Well, we should
get you out of here.

01:32.092 --> 01:33.893
Ah... ah... ah...!

01:33.928 --> 01:35.695
Ah... ah... ah...!

01:37.297 --> 01:38.098
Hey. You okay?

01:38.498 --> 01:39.699
Yeah. Take it...
take this. Help them.

01:40.100 --> 01:42.102
Ah... agh... no...

01:42.137 --> 01:43.703
ashlocke, no!

01:43.738 --> 01:45.670
Agh.

01:45.705 --> 01:47.707
You tried to
steal me from gabriel.

01:47.742 --> 01:50.110
That was a stupid mistake.

